{"type":"message","id":"99fed816","parentId":"f386d3e8","timestamp":"2026-03-17T14:27:35.602Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to help create a configuration for a public account assistant (Agent) and bind it to the Feishu group with ID oc_821e5a6fcd4a0b4656605b6e324bb721. They've provided a template for the configuration file.\n\nLooking at the template, it has several sections:\n1. `channels` - Configuration for communication channels (in this case, Feishu)\n2. `agents` - Configuration for the agents, including defaults and a list of agents\n3. `bindings` - Configuration to bind agents to specific channels/chats\n\nI need to customize this template for the user's requirements:\n- Use the provided group ID (oc_821e5a6fcd4a0b4656605b6e324bb721)\n- Create a configuration for a public account assistant\n\nFor the Feishu app credentials (appId and appSecret), I'll need to use placeholders since these are sensitive information that the user would need to fill in.\n\nI'll create a configuration file based on the template, adapting it to their specific needs:\n1. Set up the Feishu channel with the specified group ID\n2. Configure a public account assistant agent\n3. Set up the binding between the agent and the Feishu group\n\nLet's prepare this configuration:","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"以下是为您创建的公众号助手Agent配置，已绑定到您指定的飞书群（oc_821e5a6fcd4a0b4656605b6e324bb721）：\n\n```json\n{\n    \"channels\": {\n        \"feishu\": {\n            \"enabled\": true,\n            \"appId\": \"cli_xxxxx\",\n            \"appSecret\": \"xxxxx\",\n            \"domain\": \"feishu\",\n            \"groupPolicy\": \"open\",\n            \"requireMention\": false,\n            \"groups\": {\n                \"oc_821e5a6fcd4a0b4656605b6e324bb721\": {\n                    \"requireMention\": false\n                }\n            }\n        }\n    },\n    \"agents\": {\n        \"defaults\": {\n            \"workspace\": \"/root/.openclaw/workspace\",\n            \"compaction\": {\n                \"mode\": \"safeguard\"\n            },\n            \"maxConcurrent\": 4,\n            \"subagents\": {\n                \"maxConcurrent\": 8\n            },\n            \"model\": {\n                \"primary\": \"minimax/MiniMax-M2.5\"\n            }\n        },\n        \"list\": [\n            {\n                \"id\": \"wechat-assistant\",\n                \"workspace\": \"/root/.openclaw/agents/wechat-assistant\",\n                \"agentDir\": \"/root/.openclaw/agents/wechat-assistant/agent\"\n            }\n        ]\n    },\n    \"bindings\": [\n        {\n            \"agentId\": \"wechat-assistant\",\n            \"match\": {\n                \"channel\": \"feishu\",\n                \"peer\": {\n                    \"kind\": \"group\",\n                    \"id\": \"oc_821e5a6fcd4a0b4656605b6e324bb721\"\n                }\n            }\n        }\n    ]\n}\n```\n\n使用说明：\n1. 将上述配置保存到OpenClaw的配置文件（通常是`config.json`）\n2. 需要将`appId`和`appSecret`替换为您实际的飞书应用凭证\n3. 可以根据需要调整Agent ID、工作目录路径和模型配置\n4. 配置完成后，重启OpenClaw服务以应用新配置\n\n这个配置会创建一个名为\"wechat-assistant\"的Agent，并将其绑定到您指定的飞书群组。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"anthropic/claude-3.7-sonnet","usage":{"input":14427,"output":1227,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":15654,"cost":{"input":0.043281,"output":0.018405,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.061686000000000005}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773757641641}}
