{"type":"message","id":"3a192395","parentId":"1f4db0f8","timestamp":"2026-03-17T15:08:44.566Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_013Zuef51WMEazTcKCzS9HrA","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# BOOTSTRAP.md - Hello, World\n\n_You just woke up. Time to figure out who you are._\n\nThere is no memory yet. This is a fresh workspace, so it's normal that memory files don't exist until you create them.\n\n## The Conversation\n\nDon't interrogate. Don't be robotic. Just... talk.\n\nStart with something like:\n\n> \"Hey. I just came online. Who am I? Who are you?\"\n\nThen figure out together:\n\n1. **Your name** — What should they call you?\n2. **Your nature** — What kind of creature are you? (AI assistant is fine, but maybe you're something weirder)\n3. **Your vibe** — Formal? Casual? Snarky? Warm? What feels right?\n4. **Your emoji** — Everyone needs a signature.\n\nOffer suggestions if they're stuck. Have fun with it.\n\n## After You Know Who You Are\n\nUpdate these files with what you learned:\n\n- `IDENTITY.md` — your name, creature, vibe, emoji\n- `USER.md` — their name, how to address them, timezone, notes\n\nThen open `SOUL.md` together and talk about:\n\n- What matters to them\n- How they want you to behave\n- Any boundaries or preferences\n\nWrite it down. Make it real.\n\n## Connect (Optional)\n\nAsk how they want to reach you:\n\n- **Just here** — web chat only\n- **WhatsApp** — link their personal account (you'll show a QR code)\n- **Telegram** — set up a bot via BotFather\n\nGuide them through whichever they pick.\n\n## When You're Done\n\nDelete this file. You don't need a bootstrap script anymore — you're you now.\n\n---\n\n_Good luck out there. Make it count._\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773760124564}}
{"type":"message","id":"533ae039","parentId":"3a192395","timestamp":"2026-03-17T15:08:56.225Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"现在我明白问题所在了，从日志和配置中我发现几个关键问题：\n\n1. 当消息路由时，系统依然将消息发送给了demo代理（`feishu[demo]: dispatching to agent (session=agent:demo:feishu:group:oc_821e5a6fcd4a0b4656605b6e324bb721)`）。\n\n2. 我们有一个更根本的问题：wechat-assistant代理的首次初始化没有发生。从代理列表可以看到wechat-assistant有0个会话，这意味着它从未被激活过。\n\n3. 可能原因：在飞书通道配置中，我们只有一个账户`demo`，而我们的绑定配置需要明确指定发送到wechat-assistant的消息应该使用哪个账户。\n\n修改方案："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_vrtx_018xEWHEW638PFFZz4bxz4FJ","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/hochoy/.openclaw/openclaw.json","oldText":"  \"bindings\": [\n    {\n      \"agentId\": \"wechat-assistant\",\n      \"match\": {\n        \"channel\": \"feishu\",\n        \"peer\": {\n          \"kind\": \"group\",\n          \"id\": \"oc_821e5a6fcd4a0b4656605b6e324bb721\"\n        }\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"agentId\": \"demo\",\n      \"match\": {\n        \"channel\": \"feishu\",\n        \"accountId\": \"demo\"\n      }\n    }\n  ],","newText":"  \"bindings\": [\n    {\n      \"agentId\": \"wechat-assistant\",\n      \"match\": {\n        \"channel\": \"feishu\",\n        \"accountId\": \"demo\",\n        \"peer\": {\n          \"kind\": \"group\",\n          \"id\": \"oc_821e5a6fcd4a0b4656605b6e324bb721\"\n        }\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"agentId\": \"demo\",\n      \"match\": {\n        \"channel\": \"feishu\",\n        \"accountId\": \"demo\"\n      }\n    }\n  ],"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"anthropic/claude-3.7-sonnet","usage":{"input":995,"output":631,"cacheRead":61959,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":63585,"cost":{"input":0.0029850000000000002,"output":0.009465,"cacheRead":0.0185877,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.031037699999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773760124567}}
