{"type":"message","id":"24cfa2c2","parentId":"16700b62","timestamp":"2026-03-17T15:33:11.369Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"配置文件已经成功修改，我已经完成了以下操作：\n\n1. 备份了原始的openclaw.json文件到openclaw.json.backup\n2. 在channels.feishu.accounts中添加了新的wechat-assistant账户配置：\n   ```json\n   \"wechat-assistant\": {\n     \"enabled\": true,\n     \"appId\": \"cli_a933cef770f85cd6\",\n     \"appSecret\": \"sJXVulDZSdf8jF9tF4VkZafE8bVsmEWU\",\n     \"connectionMode\": \"websocket\",\n     \"domain\": \"feishu\",\n     \"groupPolicy\": \"open\",\n     \"requireMention\": false,\n     \"groups\": {\n       \"oc_821e5a6fcd4a0b4656605b6e324bb721\": {\n         \"requireMention\": false\n       }\n     }\n   }\n   ```\n\n3. 修改了bindings配置，将wechat-assistant代理的accountId从\"demo\"改为\"wechat-assistant\"：\n   ```json\n   {\n     \"agentId\": \"wechat-assistant\",\n     \"match\": {\n       \"channel\": \"feishu\",\n       \"accountId\": \"wechat-assistant\",\n       \"peer\": {\n         \"kind\": \"group\",\n         \"id\": \"oc_821e5a6fcd4a0b4656605b6e324bb721\"\n       }\n     }\n   }\n   ```\n\n修改看起来完全正确。为了使这些更改生效，您需要重启OpenClaw网关：\n\n```\nopenclaw gateway stop\nopenclaw gateway\n```\n\n重启后，wechat-assistant账户将使用新配置的应用ID和密钥与飞书API通信，并且wechat-assistant代理将处理来自该账户在指定群组中的消息。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"anthropic/claude-3.7-sonnet","usage":{"input":1845,"output":494,"cacheRead":68098,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":70437,"cost":{"input":0.005535,"output":0.00741,"cacheRead":0.0204294,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0333744}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773761580966}}
